comments: Irving (BKN) makes contact to Beal's (WAS) body during his driving shot attempt.
Brown (BKN) wraps Hachimura (WAS) in the post and affects his ability to receive the pass.
Bertans (WAS) makes contact with Durant (BKN) as he cuts through the lane and the contact affects his FOM.
Bertans (WAS) moves alongside of Harris's (BKN) path to the basket and marginal body contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Durant (BKN) makes marginal contact to Westbrook's (WAS) arm during his driving shot attempt, that does not affect his play at the basket.
Smith (WAS) makes marginal contact to the body of Irving (BKN) at the start of the drive, but does not affect his SQBR.
Westbrook (WAS) commits a take foul on Green (BKN).
Bertans (WAS) commits a take foul on Irving (BKN).
Matthews (WAS) remains in bounds when he steals the throw-in pass.
Irving (BKN) leaves the designated throw-in spot, taking more than one step to the left before making the inbound pass.  From available angles, Bonga (WAS) also appears to step on the boundary line.
Hachimura (WAS) makes incidental contact with Luwawu-Cabarrot (BKN) following the release of his shot attempt near the rim.
Green (BKN) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
